      &lt;img alt="The Nintendo Family Computer Classic Edition and Super Famicom Classic Edition consoles pictured next to each one’s logo." src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/AnRPF1_mPtTyrcvWZEFYQZUW1AQ=/1x0:1000x666/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73607738/classicedition.0.jpg" /&gt;
