  &lt;p id="Qxht4X"&gt;You can now preorder these modular jackets designed by Jony Ive. The new product from Apple’s former chief design officer is a collaboration between his design company, &lt;a href="https://www.lovefrom.com/"&gt;LoveFrom&lt;/a&gt;, and the French fashion brand Moncler. Pieces in the &lt;a href="https://go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.moncler.com%2Fen-us%2Fsir-jony-ive-collaboration.html&amp;amp;referrer=theverge.com&amp;amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2024%2F9%2F24%2F24253225%2Fjony-ive-lovefrom-moncler-collection-launches" rel="sponsored nofollow noopener" target="_blank"&gt;LoveFrom, Moncler collection&lt;/a&gt; &lt;em&gt;start&lt;/em&gt; at &lt;a href="https://go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.moncler.com%2Fen-us%2Fmen%2Fouterwear%2Fwindbreakers-and-raincoats%2Flovefrom-moncler-parka-light-blue-J20961C00003M462070C.html&amp;amp;referrer=theverge.com&amp;amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2024%2F9%2F24%2F24253225%2Fjony-ive-lovefrom-moncler-collection-launches" rel="sponsored nofollow noopener" target="_blank"&gt;$2,440 for the parka&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.moncler.com%2Fen-us%2Fmen%2Fouterwear%2Fwindbreakers-and-raincoats%2Flovefrom-moncler-field-jacket-white-ivory-J20961B00001M4620041.html&amp;amp;referrer=theverge.com&amp;amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2024%2F9%2F24%2F24253225%2Fjony-ive-lovefrom-moncler-collection-launches" rel="sponsored nofollow noopener" target="_blank"&gt;$2,575 for the field jacket&lt;/a&gt;, and &lt;a href="https://go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.moncler.com%2Fen-us%2Fmen%2Fouterwear%2Fshort-down-jackets%2Flovefrom-moncler-moncore-down-jacket-light-yellow-J20961A00004597JY110.html&amp;amp;referrer=theverge.com&amp;amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2024%2F9%2F24%2F24253225%2Fjony-ive-lovefrom-moncler-collection-launches" rel="sponsored nofollow noopener" target="_blank"&gt;$3,115 for the down jacket&lt;/a&gt;. The &lt;a href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/6/24237784/from-this-angle-jony-ives-new-luxury-jacket-looks-like-the-stuff-of-nightmares"&gt;dashing orange poncho&lt;/a&gt; doesn’t appear to be available yet.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p id="f1d1t8"&gt;The sartorial statement pieces (&lt;em&gt;Vogue&lt;/em&gt; is &lt;a href="https://www.vogue.com/article/lovefrom-moncler"&gt;hailing them&lt;/a&gt; as the “season’s most functional outerwear”) will ship on October 10th. But you might want to be quick about it; most of the white versions are already sold out.&lt;/p&gt;
